PN,37501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,FA mother who killed her baby daughter
OL,7,Fby fracturing her skull "took a bath
OL,8,Fand bought a lottery ticket from a
OL,9,Fshop before taking her to hospital", a
OL,10,Fcourt has heard.
OL,12,FSarah Ngaba, 32, was jailed in 2021
OL,13,Fafter she caused "catastrophic
OL,14,Finjuries" to her seven-week-old
OL,15,Fdaughter, Eliza, leaving her
OL,16,F"profoundly disabled".
OL,18,FEliza died on 15 August 2022, when she
OL,19,Fwas two-years-old.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,FNgaba, from Briarwood in Telford,
OL,7,Fdenies murdering her baby daughter -
OL,8,Fclaiming instead that she is guilty of
OL,9,Finfanticide.
OL,11,FJurors at Birmingham Crown Court were
OL,12,Ftold today (Monday 11 May) the sole
OL,13,Fissue for them to decide is whether
OL,14,Fthe balance of Ngaba's mind was
OL,15,Fdisturbed at the time of the attack,
OL,16,Fand if that disturbance was partly
OL,17,Fcaused by a failure to fully recover
OL,18,Ffrom the effects of giving birth.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,FOpening the case against Ngaba on
OL,7,FMonday, prosecutor Jonas Hankin KC
OL,8,Fsaid Eliza died aged two in August
OL,9,F2022 from an infection after her
OL,10,Finjuries left her vulnerable.
OL,12,FThe court heard Eliza was born in
OL,13,FHomerton Hospital in east London on
OL,14,FSeptember 19 2019 because Ngaba, who
OL,15,Fwas living in Shropshire, wanted to be
OL,16,Fnear family members during childbirth.
OL,18,FAfter Ngaba had returned to Telford,
OL,19,Fthe court heard, Eliza was taken to
OL,20,Fhospital after being attacked in
OL,21,FNovember 2019 - at seven-weeks-old.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,FMr Hankin told the court Ngaba,
OL,7,Fformerly of Briarwood in Brookside,
OL,8,FTelford, was previously convicted of
OL,9,Fcausing grievous bodily harm.
OL,11,FThe Crown's KC said it was agreed that
OL,12,Fhead injuries inflicted by Ngaba were
OL,13,F"a cause" of Eliza's death as they had
OL,14,Fleft her profoundly disabled and
OL,15,Fvulnerable to severe complications
OL,16,Ffrom infection, including death.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,FMr Hankin said: "That is what happened
OL,7,F` she died from a respiratory
OL,8,Finfection, but she would not have died
OL,9,Ffrom that infection had she not been
OL,10,Frendered vulnerable by the injuries
OL,11,Finflicted by her mother.
OL,13,F"There is, therefore, no dispute that
OL,14,Fthe defendant unlawfully caused Eliza
OL,15,FNgaba's death and she intended to
OL,16,Fcause her really serious harm.
OL,26,@nD@QOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,F"The only issue in this trial is
OL,7,Fwhether the defence of infanticide
OL,8,Fapplies. If it does, the defendant is
OL,9,Fguilty of infanticide. If it does not,
OL,10,Fshe is guilty of murder."
OL,12,FMr Hankin told the court a witness who
OL,13,Fsaw Eliza on a video call on the
OL,14,Fmorning of November 13 2019 "could see
OL,15,Fthat her body was shaking".
OL,17,FThe man advised Ngaba to take Eliza to
OL,18,Fhospital straight away but the
OL,19,Fdefendant said she needed to have a
OL,20,Fbath and did not call an ambulance,
OL,21,Fthe court heard.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@YO]vD@]OUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,FMr Hankin added: "Instead at 8.13am
OL,7,Fshe rang a taxi company.
OL,9,F"She was told that no taxi was
OL,10,Favailable until 8.50am and that, if
OL,11,Fshe needed to get to hospital sooner,
OL,12,Fshe would have to make alternative
OL,13,Farrangements.
OL,15,F"Despite that she settled for the taxi
OL,16,Fat 8.50am."
OL,26,@nD@ROUqD@AOUwD@AOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,FDoorbell footage caught Ngaba leaving
OL,7,Fher flat at 8.40am, while footage from
OL,8,Fa local supermarket at 8.59am showed
OL,9,Fher buying a lottery ticket and
OL,10,Fobtaining cashback.
OL,12,FThe taxi driver, Mr Hankin said,
OL,13,Farrived at 9.05am and described the
OL,14,Fdefendant as being very calm and not
OL,15,Fseeming worried.
OL,17,F"When they arrived at hospital, she
OL,18,Fwas calm and did not rush," Mr Hankin
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,FMr Hankin said of the defendant's
OL,7,Falleged behaviour at the hospital: "In
OL,8,Ftriage and afterwards, staff described
OL,9,Fthe defendant as annoyed, detached and
OL,10,Fconcerned about housing rather than
OL,11,Fher baby's medical emergency."
OL,13,FThe prosecutor continued: "The
OL,14,Fprosecution says that this sequence of
OL,15,Fevents is important.
OL,17,F"Eliza was visibly shaking. The
OL,18,Fdefendant was told to take her to A&E.
OL,19,FAn ambulance was suggested. She didn't
OL,20,Fcall one.
OL,26,@oD@dOUsD@^O]uD@[OUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,F"She chose to bathe and dress first,
OL,7,Faccepted a delayed taxi, went to a
OL,8,Fsupermarket, bought a lottery ticket,
OL,9,Ftravelled calmly to hospital, and did
OL,10,Fnot even rush when she got there.
OL,12,F"That evidence is difficult to
OL,13,Freconcile with the suggestion that the
OL,14,Fassault on Eliza was the product of an
OL,15,Facute childbirth-caused disturbance of
OL,16,Fmind.
OL,18,F"It is more consistent with a lack of
OL,19,Furgency, with detachment, self-
OL,20,Fconcern, and a failure simply to
OL,21,Fprioritise her daughter's welfare."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,FNgaba is alleged to have told a
OL,7,Fnursing sister that Eliza had not fed
OL,8,Fsince around 5.00am and to have made
OL,9,Fno reference to her having suffered
OL,10,Fany sort of physical trauma.
OL,12,FMr Hankin told jurors: "The impression
OL,13,Fshe gave was that Eliza was simply
OL,14,Funwell.
OL,16,F"That's important because Eliza's
OL,17,Fneurological injuries were so severe
OL,18,Fthat after they had been inflicted she
OL,19,Fcould not have behaved normally,
OL,20,Finteracted normally, or fed normally.
OL,26,@tD@XOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,F"When Eliza was taken out of the pram,
OL,7,Fthe nurse immediately saw she was in a
OL,8,Fstate of collapse: pale, unresponsive,
OL,9,Fgasping and having seizures.
OL,11,F"Indeed she was concerned that Eliza
OL,12,Fwas about to die and she required
OL,13,Fimmediate emergency resuscitation."
OL,15,FThe court heard Eliza's injuries were
OL,16,Fcaused by forceful shaking "together
OL,17,Fwith a very significant impact" to the
OL,18,Fhead, causing a complex skull fracture.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@cO]xD@\OUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,FReferring to Ngaba's claim of
OL,7,Finfanticide, Mr Hankin added: "The
OL,8,Fdefence will say that, at the time of
OL,9,Fthe assault, the balance of the
OL,10,Fdefendant's mind was disturbed, and it
OL,11,Fwas disturbed at least in part because
OL,12,Fshe had not fully recovered from the
OL,13,Feffects of giving birth.
OL,15,F"The prosecution says the evidence
OL,16,Fdoes not justify such a conclusion.
OL,26,@oD@_OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778598676
OL,3,CMum accused of murder 'bought lottery
OL,4,Cticket' before taking baby to hospital
OL,6,F"The prosecution says that when the
OL,7,Fevidence is looked at carefully, the
OL,8,Ftrue picture is not one of a
OL,9,Fchildbirth-related disturbance of mind
OL,10,F` it is one of anger, frustration,
OL,11,Fresentment and a loss of self-control."
OL,13,FThe trial continues.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/14
